high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room to face the sink.
Pick up the knife on the sink.
Turn right and step forward to face the fridge.
Cut the apple in the microwave into three pieces.
Place the knife in the microwave.
Pick up the piece of the apple in the microwave.
Take a step to the right to face the fridge.
Place the apple in the top of the fridge.
Turn around and step forward to face the trash can on the floor.
Place the apple piece in the trash can on the floor.
anns.task_desc: To put an apple slice in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn around and face the sink in front of you.
Take the knife from the counter in front of you.
Turn right and face the microwave in front of you.
Open the microwave and cut the apple inside.
Place the knife in the microwave in front of you.
Take an apple slice from the microwave in front of you and close the microwave.
Turn right and face the fridge to your left.
Place the apple inside the fridge in front of you then take it out and close the fridge.
Turn around and face the green can in front of you.
Place the apple slice in the can in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold apple slice in the green can.
